{
  "stem": "4830.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So as I started to-- to see our paramilitary unit, I get into trouble with the-- the events of war much earlier than these German or Hungarian fascists.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were stationing in Csepel, Weiss Manfred factory.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was the largest ammunition and weapon factory in Central Europe, and as such it was a target for Ally air raids.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was an Ally air raid just around July the 20th, in which a very large number-- in between 800 and 2,000 aeroplanes bombed this factory very effectively.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They put the factory out of commission.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Approximately 75%, 80% of them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The factory never could produce again the way as they did previously.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But there was a very high price in human life.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Particularly, Jewish paramilitary units were very heavily affected.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The rule by the-- one of the fascist oriented chief executive officer of this factory was that in air raids, the Jews had to go out of the bunkers.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There were bunkers built in such a fashion that they could resist even direct hits.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was participating in building one together with our unit, but they had the order that Jews have to leave-- when the air raids start-- these bunkers.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we were outside in the-- still, there were shelters.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Some shelters dug in the ground and covered with a few layer of bricks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But they were of course not resisting hits.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "In this single air raid that I mentioned to you, over 10,000 young Jewish men died.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Altogether, approximately 20,000 people died in the area, and it was a major catastrophe in that sense.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The fascist minister of interior who was in charge of this came out, and he really let this chief executive officer have it.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
